.DS_Store
# Gradle / Android: every module’s build/ (root-only /build is not enough)
**/build/

# Kotlin compiler / tooling caches (e.g. under build-logic)
**/.kotlin/

# Gradle / IDE output under convention plugin (source of truth is src/main/kotlin)
build-logic/convention/bin/

# Android / JVM artifacts that sometimes land outside **/build/ (e.g. mistaken `git add .`)
*.hprof
*.apk
*.aab
*.ap_

# Captures, NDK, CMake (often under module roots)
/captures
**/captures/
.externalNativeBuild
**/.externalNativeBuild/
.cxx
**/.cxx/

# Release signing (local)
keystore.properties
*.jks
*.keystore

# Play API (never commit)
play-store-credentials.json

# Fastlane
fastlane/report.xml
fastlane/Preview.html
fastlane/screenshots
fastlane/test_output
